### collectPotentiallyDeadInstrs() {#a5ad7b5f4a7820715d589e79d06cc653c}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>void llvm::sandboxir::BottomUpVec::collectPotentiallyDeadInstrs (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/arrayref">ArrayRef</a>&lt; <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sandboxir/value">Value</a> &#42; &gt; Bndl)</>}>
After we create vectors for groups of instructions, the original instructions are potentially dead and may need to be removed.

This function helps collect these instructions (along with the pointer operands for loads/stores) so that they can be cleaned up later.

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/transforms/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/passes/bottomupvec-h/#l00051">51</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/transforms/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/include/llvm/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/passes/bottomupvec-h">BottomUpVec.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/lib/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/lib/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/passes/bottomupvec-cpp/#l00257">257</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/vectorize/lib/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/lib/transforms/vectorize/sandboxvectorizer/passes/bottomupvec-cpp">BottomUpVec.cpp</a>.
